{"tid":1398914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海港城2018年租戶零售銷售總額370億元，每日超過一億","createTime":"2019-08-03T03:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:25:57.000Z","uid":34612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4dc72db4fd2d0a1167727ca02ad099c012e2eb","tid":1398914,"uid":34612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:46:50.000Z","msg":"海港城（包括酒店部分）在2018年營業額為118.71億港元，按年升10%，營業盈利則升12%至96.78億元。租戶零售銷售總額370億元，整個物業項目在2018年底的估值為1843.89億元，酒店及會所營業額增加10%至14.76億元，服務式住宅營業額減少29%至至2.32億元，寫字樓營業額則升6%至26.34億元。商場營業額增長14%至75.29億元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba65f240ef0a5234749d3457726819e274dfb853","tid":1398914,"uid":23468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"全世界嘅名店喺晒入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a0a39455f9db28f100a79f0c269ad0ba357269","tid":1398914,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:00:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d88c18f4f8463d4ac32e38e000a3b2cb16e71ac4","tid":1398914,"uid":34612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d42c2331fa4d76aec6d327712f34add5d06b1e3","tid":1398914,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}